{"tid":1958970,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大埔男遭巨石壓斃　被發現時疑死去多時","createTime":"2020-04-05T05:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T07:51:48.000Z","uid":229185,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"021f7f8925a982d372dd04a85b7f58085e05c3c3","tid":1958970,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:50:46.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3tArrq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3tArrq.jpg&h=81399e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今（5日）上午9時半，大埔南華莆村工地一帶，有途人發現一名男子於上址被巨石壓住，沒有反應，於是報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報後到場調查，救護人員將巨石移走，男子現場證實死亡，召仵工到場把屍體舁送殮房。據了解，死者年約50歲，於上址工作，被發現時懷疑已死去多時，事件仍有待調查。"},{"pid":"0d10ad275db52ba58bf7d8582146c0354bf502af","tid":1958970,"uid":260121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:51:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196e5ad41b2ed91d480e9fa255a51ee59a96ebc4","tid":1958970,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知咩事"},{"pid":"899185f19af168ac1e23a8c659953d5b6db09acc","tid":1958970,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">起樓主底<br />\n有伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>"},{"pid":"98382cffe85895310d6099dc117faf059d08bdb9